        "text": "# Beginners guide\nBefore the Internet was born in 1983, computer networks lacked a standard method of communicating with one another. In the years since - as online communications have grown interwoven with our daily lives and revolutionised the world we live in - there remains a crucial thing we still don't have a standardised way of talking about in the digital world: you- [https://domilabs.io/beginners-guide-ssi/ domilabs.io]"
